concurrency

public IngestProcessor.Builder concurrency(int concurrency)
Sets the number of concurrent requests allowed to be executed. A value of 0 means that only a single request will be allowed to be executed. A value of 1 means 1 concurrent request is allowed to be executed while accumulating new bulk requests. Defaults to 1.

actions

public IngestProcessor.Builder actions(int actions)
Sets when to flush a new bulk request based on the number of actions currently added. Defaults to 1000. Can be set to -1 to disable it.

maxVolume

public IngestProcessor.Builder maxVolume(org.elasticsearch.common.unit.ByteSizeValue volume)
When to flush a new bulk request based on the byte volume of actions currently added. Defaults to 5mb. Can be set to -1 to disable it.

build

public IngestProcessor build()
Builds a new bulk processor.
